1
00:00:06,006 --> 00:00:07,966
[rock music playing]

2
00:00:08,591 --> 00:00:12,679
‎那么…怎么办？到底来不来？
So… what's the deal?
Are we doing this or not?

3
00:00:12,762 --> 00:00:14,055
‎我不知道 我衣服上还写着这种话
I don't know.

4
00:00:14,139 --> 00:00:15,724
‎我不知道 我衣服上还写着这种话
‎（够胆 让孩子远离毒品）
I'm literally wearing <i>this</i>.

5
00:00:16,558 --> 00:00:18,226
‎没错 让咱们够胆就试试
Yeah, they're daring us to do it.

6
00:00:18,977 --> 00:00:21,146
‎是啊 他们没考虑清楚
‎别人能解读出啥意思
Yeah, they didn't think
that messaging through.

7
00:00:21,229 --> 00:00:23,732
‎兄弟 这玩意儿算打火机吗？
Bro, does this count as a lighter?

8
00:00:23,815 --> 00:00:25,025
‎算啊
Uh, yeah.

9
00:00:26,985 --> 00:00:29,237
‎我不知道我做不做得来
‎我来自一个有名的家族
I don't know if I can do this.
I'm from a famous family.

10
00:00:29,320 --> 00:00:31,698
‎我表哥给布雷特法弗装过浴室
My cousin did Brett Favre's bathroom.

11
00:00:32,407 --> 00:00:35,243
‎不好意思 别让我又听到
‎布雷特法弗浴室那档子事
I'm sorry. I can't do
your Brett Favre bathroom story again.

12
00:00:37,078 --> 00:00:38,955
‎伙计们 咱们上保健课都学过
Guys, we learned about this
in health class.

13
00:00:39,039 --> 00:00:40,540
‎我觉得大家就应该说…
I think we should just say…

14
00:00:41,124 --> 00:00:41,958
‎哇哦
Whoa.

15
00:00:43,001 --> 00:00:45,628
‎-宝贝 你感觉到了吗？
‎-好像没有
-Babe, are you feeling it?
-I don't think so.

16
00:00:46,463 --> 00:00:49,424
‎大金刚为啥是猩猩 不是驴子？
Why is Donkey Kong
a gorilla and not a donkey?

17
00:00:51,342 --> 00:00:52,510
‎骗人的
It's a lie.

18
00:00:53,762 --> 00:00:57,057
‎他们将整个帝国建立在谎言之上
They based their entire empire on a lie.

19
00:00:59,059 --> 00:01:00,810
‎对啊 我也没啥感觉
Yeah, I'm not feeling it either.

20
00:01:05,231 --> 00:01:06,316
[snaps]

21
00:01:08,693 --> 00:01:09,694
‎有意思
Interesting.

22
00:01:10,653 --> 00:01:12,864
‎伙子 这些旧法兰绒太牛了
Dude, these old flannels are so dope.

23
00:01:13,948 --> 00:01:17,452
‎那些是我爷爷的 他娶了那谁谁
Those are my grandpa's flannels.
He's married to what's-her-name.

24
00:01:18,661 --> 00:01:21,039
‎等等…那是谁来着？
Wait… What's her name?!

25
00:01:21,998 --> 00:01:23,208
‎喂 我是谁？
Hey, who am I?

26
00:01:23,917 --> 00:01:26,002
‎你爷爷的身体
Your grandpa's body. [chuckles]

27
00:01:26,086 --> 00:01:28,797
‎刚才还在 然后没了
It was there. It was gone.

28
00:01:30,340 --> 00:01:31,341
‎就像爱情
Just like love.

29
00:01:32,383 --> 00:01:35,553
‎莉亚 你想知道大金刚的阴谋吗？
Leia, do you want to hear about
the Donkey Kong conspiracy?

30
00:01:36,471 --> 00:01:37,847
‎他是大猩猩
[whispers] He's a gorilla!

31
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:41,351
‎这有点像雪儿克罗其实不是只乌鸦
It's kinda like how Sheryl Crow
isn't actually a crow.

32
00:01:42,852 --> 00:01:43,853
‎必须的
Totally.

33
00:01:45,522 --> 00:01:47,273
‎爷爷的身体饿了
Grandpa's body's hungry.

34
00:01:49,025 --> 00:01:50,985
‎我去拿零食 你们想吃什么？
I'll get snacks. What do you guys want?

35
00:01:51,528 --> 00:01:52,570
‎葡萄干麦片
Raisin Bran.

36
00:01:53,113 --> 00:01:54,447
‎葡萄干麦片
Raisin Bran.

37
00:01:54,531 --> 00:01:55,615
‎葡萄干麦片
[both] Raisin Bran!

38
00:01:56,241 --> 00:01:57,158
‎交给我
On it.

39
00:02:00,036 --> 00:02:01,371
‎等等 我要拿啥来着？
Wait, what was I getting?

40
00:02:02,038 --> 00:02:03,456
‎一 二 三 四…
[young woman] <i>One, two, three, four!</i>

41
00:02:03,540 --> 00:02:05,125
‎在街上闲逛
<i>♪ Hangin' out down the street ♪</i>

42
00:02:05,208 --> 00:02:07,127
‎和上周没什么两样
<i>♪ The same old thing we did last week ♪</i>

43
00:02:07,210 --> 00:02:11,673
‎没什么事好做 就跟你把话说
<i>♪ Not a thing to do but talk to you ♪</i>

44
00:02:11,756 --> 00:02:12,715
‎这样挺好 这样挺好
<i>♪ We're all all right! ♪</i>

45
00:02:12,799 --> 00:02:14,509
‎这样挺好 这样挺好
<i>♪ We're all all right! ♪</i>

46
00:02:14,592 --> 00:02:17,137
‎你好 威斯康辛！
‎（90年代秀）
[young woman] <i>Hello, Wisconsin!</i>

47
00:02:18,096 --> 00:02:21,224
‎我只是…不知道晚上要干点什么了
Well, I just… I don't know
what to do with my evenings anymore

48
00:02:21,307 --> 00:02:23,476
‎这么多夏季重播
with these summer reruns.

49
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:26,980
‎要能出几集《五口之家》
‎让我弄死一口子都行
I would murder someone
for a fresh <i>Party of Five</i>.

50
00:02:27,564 --> 00:02:30,108
‎要是再让我看一遍《优雅从容》
If I have to sit through
another<i> Grace Under Fire</i> rerun,

51
00:02:30,608 --> 00:02:31,901
‎我就要放火闹事了
I'm gonna root for the fire.

52
00:02:33,153 --> 00:02:37,699
‎凯蒂 我从菜园收了第一轮的菜
Kitty, I've got the first haul
from my vegetable garden.

53
00:02:37,782 --> 00:02:38,825
[Red chuckles]

54
00:02:38,908 --> 00:02:40,535
‎让我们瞧瞧
Show us your harvest.

55
00:02:45,999 --> 00:02:48,042
‎哇！
[laughs] Wow!

56
00:02:48,626 --> 00:02:49,878
[chuckles]

57
00:02:49,961 --> 00:02:54,549
‎我要把它切成片 然后放在汉堡上
I am gonna just slice this up
and put it on some burgers.

58
00:02:55,383 --> 00:02:56,593
‎过家家的汉堡
Doll burgers.

59
00:02:57,177 --> 00:03:00,597
‎-你不在地下室 来这里做什么？
‎-实话实说呗
-What are you doing out of the basement?
-Calling it like I see it.

60
00:03:02,849 --> 00:03:05,185
‎哦 厨房在这里呐 超赞
Oh, here's the kitchen. Wild.

61
00:03:06,686 --> 00:03:07,770
‎嗨！
Hi!

62
00:03:09,022 --> 00:03:10,190
‎可不是嗨了么
Clearly.

63
00:03:11,357 --> 00:03:15,153
‎怎么样…你在楼下
‎跟新朋友玩得开心吗？
So… you having fun downstairs
with your new friends?

64
00:03:15,236 --> 00:03:17,280
‎完全是我想要的
It's everything I've ever wanted.

65
00:03:17,363 --> 00:03:18,865
‎除了葡萄干麦片
Besides Raisin Bran.

66
00:03:18,948 --> 00:03:20,533
‎家里好像没了
Oh, I think we're all out.

67
00:03:21,242 --> 00:03:22,076
‎啊？
What?!

68
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:24,287
‎但我答应要拿葡萄干麦片的
But I… I promised Raisin Bran.

69
00:03:25,205 --> 00:03:28,791
‎要是没有的话 就又没人跟我玩了
If I don't find some Raisin B,
I'm gonna be alone again!

70
00:03:29,751 --> 00:03:31,044
‎你没事吧？
Are you okay?

71
00:03:31,711 --> 00:03:35,673
‎（菜单）
[upbeat 8-bit video game music playing]

72
00:03:38,718 --> 00:03:41,054
‎谁会不愿意跟你做朋友呢？
Well, now, who wouldn't want
to be your friend?

73
00:03:41,137 --> 00:03:42,847
‎你聪明伶俐
You are smart and charming.

74
00:03:43,348 --> 00:03:46,226
‎说起来 应该给你块饼干吃
In fact, you deserve a cookie.

75
00:03:52,023 --> 00:03:53,942
‎哪个小屁孩要是敢喷你
[Red] If any of those kids give you guff,

76
00:03:54,025 --> 00:03:56,861
‎我非揪着他们衣服领子
I will grab them
by the back of their collar

77
00:03:56,945 --> 00:03:59,239
‎把他们扔出去
‎（加分！）
-and toss them into next week.
-[video game beep]

78
00:03:59,822 --> 00:04:00,823
[chuckles]

79
00:04:00,907 --> 00:04:04,160
‎没错 现在肩膀也好了 他有这本事
That's right. He can do it too,
now that his shoulder is healed.

80
00:04:04,661 --> 00:04:05,620
‎这倒是提醒我了
Which reminds me,

81
00:04:05,703 --> 00:04:08,456
‎你明天能开车送我去做理疗吧？
are you gonna be able to drive me
to physical therapy tomorrow?

82
00:04:10,166 --> 00:04:13,294
‎我要去做头发…但应该能行
Oh. I'm getting my hair done. [laughs]

83
00:04:13,378 --> 00:04:14,504
‎我要去做头发…但应该能行
But I'll make it work.

84
00:04:14,587 --> 00:04:17,590
‎赶紧跟我跳舞吧 大猩猩
Now, dance with me, you big gorilla.

85
00:04:17,674 --> 00:04:19,342
[Red laughs]

86
00:04:21,010 --> 00:04:22,178
‎好吧 聊得好爽
Okay. Good talk.

87
00:04:23,513 --> 00:04:26,057
[rock music playing]

88
00:04:27,016 --> 00:04:29,936
‎-这应该是莉亚的房间
‎-嗯 她人呢？
-I think this is Leia's room.
-Yeah. Where is she?

89
00:04:30,019 --> 00:04:31,020
[Jay] Huh.

90
00:04:32,605 --> 00:04:34,065
‎这睡衣挺朴实的
Pretty sensible sleepwear.

91
00:04:34,649 --> 00:04:37,402
‎不是吧 她有高血压
Oh no. She's got high blood pressure.

92
00:04:38,736 --> 00:04:40,405
‎这是她爷爷奶奶的房间
It's her grandparents' room.

93
00:04:43,074 --> 00:04:45,243
‎现在拿着这件睡衣觉得没意思了
Holding this has become less exciting.

94
00:04:47,829 --> 00:04:49,247
‎挖到宝了！
It's the mother lode!

95
00:04:49,914 --> 00:04:50,790
‎我要下手了
I'm goin' in.

96
00:04:52,375 --> 00:04:54,335
‎宝贝 你穿这件会很好看的
Oh, you'd look so good in this, babe.

97
00:04:55,211 --> 00:04:56,921
‎像是火辣的伐木工
Like a hot lumberjack.

98
00:04:57,714 --> 00:04:59,674
‎惹得我想在小树林跟你干坏事
Makes me wanna do stuff with you
in the woods.

99
00:04:59,757 --> 00:05:00,717
[gulps]

100
00:05:01,384 --> 00:05:02,593
‎我刚支帐篷了
I just pitched a tent.

101
00:05:03,303 --> 00:05:05,722
‎兄弟 有它就不会了
Bro, this will make it go away.

102
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:10,476
‎这个归我了
This is mine now.

103
00:05:11,352 --> 00:05:13,313
‎原来你们在我爷爷奶奶房间里
Oh, here you guys are.
In my grandparents' room.

104
00:05:13,396 --> 00:05:15,481
‎我都没敢进过这里
The room I've never dared
set foot in my whole life.

105
00:05:15,565 --> 00:05:17,984
‎-我们来这儿没问题吗？
‎-嗯 我没意见
-Is it cool that we're up here?
-Yeah, I'm cool.

106
00:05:18,067 --> 00:05:22,071
‎现在是暑假 大家开开心心
‎想做什么就做什么 对吧？
It's the summer. Let's have fun.
We should do whatever we want. Right?

107
00:05:22,155 --> 00:05:23,156
‎不对
Wrong.

108
00:05:28,161 --> 00:05:29,829
‎-拜拜了
‎-出去
-Buh-bye now.
-Get out.

109
00:05:29,912 --> 00:05:31,581
‎-回头见
‎-出去
-See you soon.
-Get out.

110
00:05:31,664 --> 00:05:33,875
‎-常来啊
‎-出去
-Don't be a stranger.
-Get out.

111
00:05:33,958 --> 00:05:35,126
‎这个糖霜多
Extra icing.

112
00:05:35,209 --> 00:05:36,836
‎那是我的
That was mine.

113
00:05:36,919 --> 00:05:40,089
‎-我们从来不锁推拉门
‎-现在开始要锁了
-We never lock the sliding door.
-We do now.

114
00:05:42,717 --> 00:05:44,177
‎对不起 爷爷
I'm sorry, Grandpa.

115
00:05:44,260 --> 00:05:47,180
‎听着 这种阵仗 我见识过
Look, I lived through this once before.

116
00:05:47,263 --> 00:05:49,474
‎以后要先给你们立点规矩
And I'm not gonna do this again
without some ground rules.

117
00:05:49,557 --> 00:05:51,851
‎告诉你那帮朋友
So you tell your friends,

118
00:05:51,934 --> 00:05:56,105
‎别想吃我的 喝我的
no eating my food, no drinking my drinks,

119
00:05:56,189 --> 00:05:57,774
‎要敢进我房间 我非打他们屁股不可
and if they go in my room,

120
00:05:58,483 --> 00:06:00,651
‎要敢进我房间 我非打他们屁股不可
my foot goes in their ass.

121
00:06:01,402 --> 00:06:04,864
‎人们在卧室里放了各种私人物品
You know, people keep all kinds of
private things in their bedroom.

122
00:06:04,947 --> 00:06:10,495
‎我爸在他们夫妻的房间
‎藏了一条鞭子防贼
My father kept a whip hidden
in my parents' room in case of a burglar.

123
00:06:10,578 --> 00:06:14,749
‎他还有一副毛茸茸的手铐 以防…
Also, he had a pair of furry handcuffs,
in case…

124
00:06:17,377 --> 00:06:18,378
‎我的神啊
Oh dear lord.

125
00:06:19,921 --> 00:06:21,672
‎他们好像觉得我很酷
I think they think I'm cooler than I am.

126
00:06:21,756 --> 00:06:23,716
‎自从我来到这里之后 一切都很棒
Since I got here, it's been amazing.

127
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,675
‎我们抽了…火腿
We smoked…

128
00:06:25,510 --> 00:06:26,344
‎我们抽了…火腿
a ham,

129
00:06:27,011 --> 00:06:28,388
‎还开了…
and we tapped a…

130
00:06:29,597 --> 00:06:30,431
‎火腿
a ham.

131
00:06:32,016 --> 00:06:35,103
‎我担心他们期待还有火腿 知道吗？
I'm worried they're expecting
more ham, you know?

132
00:06:36,521 --> 00:06:39,232
‎这可要不少火腿呢
That's an awful lot of ham.

133
00:06:40,066 --> 00:06:42,610
‎我觉得你给自己太大压力了
Honey, I think you're putting
too much pressure on yourself.

134
00:06:42,693 --> 00:06:45,405
‎何不邀请他们
‎哪天晚上来一起看电影呢？
Why don't you invite them back
for a movie night?

135
00:06:45,488 --> 00:06:47,031
‎没人在听我说话吗？
Is nobody listening to me?

136
00:06:48,866 --> 00:06:51,619
‎奶奶 我不确定
‎电影之夜？不会无聊吗？
I don't know, Grandma.
A movie night? It's not boring?

137
00:06:51,702 --> 00:06:53,871
‎不啊 会很好玩的
No, it'll be fun.

138
00:06:53,955 --> 00:06:55,373
‎就明天吧
We'll do it tomorrow.

139
00:06:55,456 --> 00:06:58,126
‎我们租卷带子 再做一根火腿
We'll rent a movie and make a ham.

140
00:06:58,209 --> 00:07:00,420
‎既然你们心心念念想要
Since you kids are so obsessed with it.

141
00:07:01,587 --> 00:07:04,006
[rock music playing]

142
00:07:04,090 --> 00:07:05,550
‎我去开门！
-[knocking]
-I'll get it!

143
00:07:08,886 --> 00:07:11,264
‎你们哪个冲我家孩子吼来着？
Hey, which one of you yelled at my kids?

144
00:07:11,931 --> 00:07:13,141
‎雷德 找你的
Red, it's for you.

145
00:07:13,933 --> 00:07:16,561
‎我不知道哪个是你家娃 但他们活该
I don't know which ones are yours,
but they deserved it.

146
00:07:16,644 --> 00:07:19,480
‎是格温和内特 谢了 我吼得都烦死了
Oh, that's Gwen and Nate, and thanks.

147
00:07:19,564 --> 00:07:21,065
‎是格温和内特 谢了 我吼得都烦死了
I'm sick of yelling at them.

148
00:07:21,149 --> 00:07:24,110
‎昨天 我抓到内特在房顶滑旱冰
Yesterday, I caught Nate
on the roof trying on rollerblades.

149
00:07:24,193 --> 00:07:26,112
‎我怀他十个月
I was pregnant with him for ten months.

150
00:07:26,195 --> 00:07:28,948
‎医生说没事 但我觉得够呛
The doctor said it was okay,
but I don't think it was.

151
00:07:30,783 --> 00:07:33,411
‎你搬到隔壁了 是吧？
You moved in next door, right?

152
00:07:33,494 --> 00:07:38,207
‎我上周跟你挥手
‎但你正拿着水管子洗头发 所以…
I waved at you last week, but you were
washing your hair with the hose, so…

153
00:07:38,291 --> 00:07:41,085
‎我叫凯蒂 这位是雷德
[laughs] I am Kitty and this is Red.

154
00:07:41,169 --> 00:07:43,880
‎我是雪莉 是啊 我的淋浴坏了
Oh, I'm Sherri.
And, yeah, my shower head's broke.

155
00:07:43,963 --> 00:07:47,425
‎事实证明
‎它承受不了两个大人的重量
Turns out it can't support
the weight of two fully grown adults.

156
00:07:48,009 --> 00:07:51,596
‎瞧瞧你跟你老公 这么有情趣
Oh, well, look at you and your hubby
keeping things saucy.

157
00:07:51,679 --> 00:07:53,848
‎老公滚蛋了
Oh. Actually, the hubby's
out of the picture,

158
00:07:53,931 --> 00:07:56,934
‎但跟我约会的男人
‎一直吵吵着要一起住
but the guy I've been seeing
is talking about us moving in together.

159
00:07:57,018 --> 00:07:58,603
‎-你们交往多久了？
‎-两个星期
How long have you been seeing each other?

160
00:07:58,686 --> 00:07:59,812
‎-你们交往多久了？
‎-两个星期
Two weeks.

161
00:07:59,896 --> 00:08:02,231
‎刚两个星期 他已经想搬进来了？
Two weeks and he already wants to move in?

162
00:08:02,315 --> 00:08:05,943
‎对 他有点黏人 我应该把他甩了
Yeah, he's kinda clingy.
I should probably break things off.

163
00:08:06,027 --> 00:08:10,114
‎太可惜了 他要啥有啥
‎长得帅 工作好 还有辆蓝色米亚达
It's too bad. He's got it all.
Good looks, good job, blue Miata.

164
00:08:10,990 --> 00:08:13,868
‎你们介意我
‎借用微波炉热一下这个吗？
Hey. You guys mind
if I pop this in your microwave?

165
00:08:13,951 --> 00:08:15,786
‎我家的微波炉 一个钟头都搞不定
It'll take a hour if I use mine.

166
00:08:16,871 --> 00:08:18,331
‎当然 在厨房
Sure, sure. It's in the kitchen.

167
00:08:18,414 --> 00:08:21,167
‎凯蒂 你真贴心 雷德嘛…
Oh. Kitty, you're a sweetheart. And Red…

168
00:08:22,043 --> 00:08:23,002
‎嗯
Yeah.

169
00:08:25,296 --> 00:08:28,466
‎她的包里什么都有
She has all sorts of things in that bag.

170
00:08:28,549 --> 00:08:31,886
‎是啊 垃圾一满兜
Yeah, she's like a trashy Mary Poppins.

171
00:08:31,969 --> 00:08:36,390
[rock music playing]

172
00:08:36,474 --> 00:08:38,392
‎也许你想太多了
Maybe you're overthinking this.

173
00:08:38,476 --> 00:08:41,979
‎我们能快进到你选电影的环节吗？
Could we fast-forward
to the part where you pick a movie?

174
00:08:42,563 --> 00:08:43,898
Oh! [laughing]

175
00:08:43,981 --> 00:08:46,567
‎“快进”！真妙
"Fast-forward"! That is clever!

176
00:08:46,651 --> 00:08:48,694
‎我应该把这段子寄去《雷诺今夜秀》
I should send that in to Leno.

177
00:08:48,778 --> 00:08:52,073
‎关键是我不能挑
‎大家都觉得傻乎乎的片子
It's really important I don't pick
something everyone will think is dorky.

178
00:08:52,156 --> 00:08:55,034
‎你选的才不会傻乎乎呢
Well, you couldn't pick something dorky
if you tried.

179
00:08:55,117 --> 00:08:58,955
‎-来吧 你最喜欢哪部电影？
‎-《威鲸闯天关》吧
-Come on. What's your favorite movie?
-Um, I guess <i>Free Willy</i>.

180
00:08:59,539 --> 00:09:01,707
‎妈呀 傻冒泡儿了！
Whoa. Dork city!

181
00:09:01,791 --> 00:09:03,042
[laughs]

182
00:09:03,626 --> 00:09:04,460
[grunts]

183
00:09:05,044 --> 00:09:06,546
‎我去找人帮忙
I'm gonna go ask for some help.

184
00:09:08,881 --> 00:09:11,717
‎-举起手来！
‎-要钱拿走 全拿走
-Stick 'em up!
-Aah! Take my money! Take everything!

185
00:09:11,801 --> 00:09:15,304
‎我老板从来不锁车
‎她的车牌上写着“刷片荡妇”
My boss never locks her car!
Her license plate says MOVIESLUT!

186
00:09:15,388 --> 00:09:18,474
‎是很难听 我也不想说
‎就是告诉你一声
I know. I don't want to say it.
I'm just letting you know.

187
00:09:18,558 --> 00:09:19,892
‎求你了…
Please…

188
00:09:19,976 --> 00:09:22,478
‎杰伊 是我啦 逗你玩呢
Jay, it's just me. I was joking.

189
00:09:23,437 --> 00:09:24,814
‎哦
Oh. Yeah.

190
00:09:24,897 --> 00:09:25,815
[clears throat]

191
00:09:25,898 --> 00:09:27,275
‎我也是
Me too. [sniffles]

192
00:09:27,358 --> 00:09:28,192
‎真够逗的
Good one.

193
00:09:29,277 --> 00:09:31,362
‎没想到你在这里打工
-I, um, didn't know you worked here.
-Oh.

194
00:09:31,445 --> 00:09:34,282
‎混演艺圈这事 我不想太高调
Well, I didn't want to brag about
being in show business.

195
00:09:35,199 --> 00:09:36,701
‎对哈
Right. Um…

196
00:09:36,784 --> 00:09:39,745
‎我想为电影之夜选一部酷酷的电影
So I'm trying to find
a cool movie for movie night,

197
00:09:39,829 --> 00:09:42,331
‎我也不是超级担心啦
and, not that I'm super worried about it
or anything,

198
00:09:42,415 --> 00:09:44,250
‎那是哪部片子来着？
but what's that one movie?

199
00:09:44,333 --> 00:09:48,462
‎就一群人 在那里 那谁谁的？
You know, with all the guys
and the place and… the guys?

200
00:09:49,046 --> 00:09:50,923
‎-《疯狂店员》？
‎-对的 《疯狂店员》！
-Uh, <i>Clerks</i>?
<i>-Clerks</i>, yes!

201
00:09:51,007 --> 00:09:53,843
‎我去！我超爱《疯狂店员》
‎凯文史密斯 多棒啊？
Get out! I love<i> Clerks.</i>
Kevin Smith, right?

202
00:09:54,427 --> 00:09:57,638
‎就是 他在里面超性感的
Oh yeah! He was so sexy in that.

203
00:09:58,514 --> 00:10:00,725
‎哦 好吧
Okay. Cool.

204
00:10:01,309 --> 00:10:04,020
‎我看看有没有哈 看看…
Uh, well, let's see if I have it.
Let's see…

205
00:10:06,272 --> 00:10:07,481
‎好烦 租出去了
Ah, crud, it's out.

206
00:10:08,065 --> 00:10:10,526
‎有人霸占六个星期没还呢
Some guy has had it for six weeks.

207
00:10:11,152 --> 00:10:13,279
‎杰伊 来厕所帮我一下
Yo, Jay. I need your help in the bathroom.

208
00:10:13,362 --> 00:10:15,615
‎《魔岛仙踪》的火山喷了
It's a<i> Joe Versus the Volcano </i>situation.

209
00:10:17,158 --> 00:10:18,159
‎回头聊 妹子
Later, girl.

210
00:10:23,289 --> 00:10:25,666
‎-来吧 奶奶 我们得走了
‎-等一下
-Come on, Grandma. We gotta go.
-Oh, just a sec.

211
00:10:25,750 --> 00:10:28,794
‎戴夫牧师 是我 凯蒂！
‎（只限成人）
Pastor Dave, it's Kitty!

212
00:10:28,878 --> 00:10:31,922
‎上次百乐餐之后就没再见你呢
I haven't seen you since the potluck.

213
00:10:33,007 --> 00:10:34,884
‎这也太不圣洁了
That was very unholy.

214
00:10:35,384 --> 00:10:38,220
[rock music playing]

215
00:10:39,096 --> 00:10:41,057
‎嗨 福尔曼先生
Hey, Mr. Forman.

216
00:10:41,140 --> 00:10:43,476
‎看看我在你的迷你菜园里发现了什么
Look what I found
in your garden of tiny vegetables.

217
00:10:43,559 --> 00:10:44,935
‎小黄瓜
Baby cucumber.

218
00:10:45,019 --> 00:10:46,646
‎给我
Give me that.

219
00:10:47,563 --> 00:10:49,523
‎这是正常尺寸
That is normal-sized.

220
00:10:50,816 --> 00:10:53,569
‎别觉得丢脸
‎也许它只是蔫巴了 还没硬起来
Don't be embarrassed.
Maybe it's a grower, not a shower.

221
00:10:55,696 --> 00:10:59,659
‎说起来
‎我是来找你聊聊法兰绒衬衣的事
Anyway, I came by
to talk to you about your flannels.

222
00:11:00,242 --> 00:11:01,243
‎能给我一件吗？
Can I have one?

223
00:11:01,327 --> 00:11:02,161
‎为啥？
Why?

224
00:11:02,995 --> 00:11:07,500
‎我女朋友说我穿着可帅
‎其实我有点高攀不上她
My girlfriend said I looked good in it,
and she's kinda out of my league.

225
00:11:07,583 --> 00:11:10,127
‎但我非常爱她 我想让她开心
But I love her so much,
and I want to keep her happy.

226
00:11:10,211 --> 00:11:11,087
‎真不错
That's sweet.

227
00:11:11,170 --> 00:11:14,882
‎我和第一任女友也有过类似经历
I had a similar thing
with my first girlfriend.

228
00:11:16,300 --> 00:11:17,927
‎你知道她叫什么吗？
You know what her name was?

229
00:11:18,010 --> 00:11:19,387
‎出去
Get out.

230
00:11:20,846 --> 00:11:21,847
‎遵命 先生
Yes, sir.

231
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:23,891
‎嘿 邻居
Hey, neighbor.

232
00:11:26,936 --> 00:11:29,188
‎凯蒂说我家淋浴修好之前
Kitty said until I get
my shower situation fixed,

233
00:11:29,271 --> 00:11:31,357
‎我可以来这里搓搓洗洗
I can rinse my nooks and crannies
over here.

234
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:33,901
‎这里也是我家
Well, this is my house too.

235
00:11:33,984 --> 00:11:37,697
‎回你自己家搓搓洗洗去
So you can just take your crannies home.

236
00:11:37,780 --> 00:11:39,740
‎我还得借把剃刀
I'm gonna need to borrow a razor too.

237
00:11:39,824 --> 00:11:41,951
‎蓝色米亚达约我去“胡塞餐厅”吃晚餐
Blue Miata is taking me
to dinner at Houlihan's.

238
00:11:42,034 --> 00:11:44,829
‎有人愿意在“胡塞餐厅”花大钱
‎你可得把毛毛刮干净
When a guy springs for Houlihan's,
you gotta whack the weeds.

239
00:11:44,912 --> 00:11:46,414
[rock music playing]

240
00:11:47,206 --> 00:11:48,916
‎你确定我们可以
Are you sure it's okay

241
00:11:48,999 --> 00:11:51,836
‎就这么闯进别人家要录像带哇？
that we're just showing up
at somebody's house to get a movie?

242
00:11:51,919 --> 00:11:53,713
‎奶奶 我别无选择
I'm out of options here, Grandma.

243
00:11:53,796 --> 00:11:57,466
‎如果我们被杀怎么办？
‎谁惦记着给慢炖锅关火啊？
What if we get murdered?
Who's gonna turn off the Crock-Pot?

244
00:12:00,136 --> 00:12:01,512
-[doorbell chimes]
-[Kitty sighs]

245
00:12:04,181 --> 00:12:05,391
‎老天！
Aw, man!

246
00:12:08,519 --> 00:12:10,521
‎万圣节又来搞偷袭了
Halloween snuck up on me again.

247
00:12:10,604 --> 00:12:13,065
‎听着 我可没什么糖块
Hey, listen. I don't have any candy, man,

248
00:12:13,149 --> 00:12:15,359
‎但我有几根火柴
‎还有一张1975年的停车票
but I do have some matches

249
00:12:15,443 --> 00:12:18,446
‎但我有几根火柴
‎还有一张1975年的停车票
and a parking ticket from 1975.

250
00:12:20,156 --> 00:12:22,158
‎利奥 嗨
Leo. Hi.

251
00:12:22,241 --> 00:12:23,868
‎你不认得我了吗？
Don't you recognize me?

252
00:12:23,951 --> 00:12:25,244
‎认得
I do.

253
00:12:25,911 --> 00:12:30,583
‎对呀 你打扮得像凯蒂
‎有房子有头发那个女的
Yeah. You're dressed like Kitty,
the lady with the house and the hair.

254
00:12:31,208 --> 00:12:32,710
‎这身打扮绝了
Killer costume, man.

255
00:12:33,419 --> 00:12:35,755
‎你是不是租了电影《疯狂店员》
‎而且没有还？
Did you rent the movie <i>Clerks</i>
and not return it?

256
00:12:36,589 --> 00:12:37,882
‎你们是警察吗？
Are you guys cops?

257
00:12:37,965 --> 00:12:39,884
‎利奥 集中注意力
Leo, focus.

258
00:12:39,967 --> 00:12:42,428
‎你们如果要找利奥集中注意力
Hey, if you cops are looking
for Leo Focus,

259
00:12:42,511 --> 00:12:44,346
‎那你们找错人了
you got the wrong guy, man.

260
00:12:45,723 --> 00:12:47,308
‎拜托 利奥 这很重要
Please, Leo. This is important.

261
00:12:47,391 --> 00:12:50,311
‎知道我最近喜欢刷啥片子不？
You know what I've been watching
a ton of lately?

262
00:12:51,353 --> 00:12:52,396
‎《真实世界》
<i>The Real World</i>.

263
00:12:52,897 --> 00:12:54,356
‎想想看
Because think about it.

264
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:57,902
‎如果他们演的是真实世界
‎那这些又是啥？
If that's the real world, what's all this?

265
00:13:00,070 --> 00:13:02,156
‎这法子可能行不通
This might be a dead end.

266
00:13:04,450 --> 00:13:07,244
‎等等 利奥 今天就是万圣节
Wait. Leo, it <i>is</i> Halloween.

267
00:13:07,328 --> 00:13:09,747
‎你知道我想要的其实是什么吗？
And you know what I really want
instead of candy?

268
00:13:09,830 --> 00:13:11,749
‎《疯狂店员》的录影带
The movie <i>Clerks</i>.

269
00:13:12,333 --> 00:13:14,710
‎我勒个去！我正好有一卷
Crazy! I got a copy.

270
00:13:15,878 --> 00:13:17,046
‎我去拿
I'll get it for you.

271
00:13:17,797 --> 00:13:20,841
‎-等等 你怎么认识这个人的？
‎-他只是…他很…
-Wait. So how do you know this guy?
-Oh, he just… He's…

272
00:13:20,925 --> 00:13:23,010
‎就那样啦 他就是
It's the usual.
You know, he's an older man

273
00:13:23,093 --> 00:13:27,598
‎你爸和他朋友年轻时候
‎经常一起玩的老家伙
who used to hang out with your dad
and his friends when they were teenagers.

274
00:13:30,810 --> 00:13:31,811
‎不会的
Nah.

275
00:13:32,853 --> 00:13:34,814
‎有事儿他们会出声的
They would have said something.

276
00:13:35,314 --> 00:13:37,775
‎好了 你们就是要录影带的警察？
Okay, are you the cops
looking for a movie?

277
00:13:38,359 --> 00:13:39,235
‎对 没错
Yes, we are.

278
00:13:41,237 --> 00:13:43,781
‎-万圣节快乐
‎-谢谢
-Happy Halloween, man.
-Thank you. Thank you.

279
00:13:48,244 --> 00:13:49,119
‎原来你在这儿呢
There you are.

280
00:13:49,203 --> 00:13:52,248
‎莉亚和我一下午可开心了
Leia and I had such a fun afternoon.

281
00:13:52,331 --> 00:13:55,376
‎凯蒂 咱们家被袭击了
Kitty, this house is under attack.

282
00:13:55,459 --> 00:13:58,045
‎到处都是半大小孩儿
There are teenagers everywhere

283
00:13:58,128 --> 00:14:02,591
‎还有一个半裸女在我家到处招摇
and a half-naked lady
swinging her bits around my house.

284
00:14:03,175 --> 00:14:05,636
‎太好了 雪莉来洗澡了
Oh good. Sherri's using the shower.

285
00:14:05,719 --> 00:14:10,808
‎你怎么又找人来家里捣乱？
Why did you open our house to chaos again?

286
00:14:10,891 --> 00:14:15,020
‎原本好好的 笨蛋都滚蛋了！
We had it made.
All the dumbasses were gone!

287
00:14:16,564 --> 00:14:18,065
‎我有点想念他们
Well, I miss them.

288
00:14:18,774 --> 00:14:21,527
‎雷德 我感觉家里太安静了
It's been too quiet
around here for me, Red.

289
00:14:22,111 --> 00:14:23,779
‎那就养只鹦鹉
Well, then, get a parrot!

290
00:14:24,280 --> 00:14:27,950
‎如果还嫌不够聒噪 就把你姐妹叫来
And if that's not enough squawkin'
for you, invite your sister.

291
00:14:28,033 --> 00:14:30,619
‎我挺享受莉亚来过暑假的
I like having Leia visit for the summer.

292
00:14:30,703 --> 00:14:32,162
‎家里又有生气了
The house is alive again.

293
00:14:32,246 --> 00:14:36,876
‎那天 我进厕所一看
‎有人尿完没放马桶盖
The other day, I walked into the bathroom,
someone had tinkled, left the seat up,

294
00:14:36,959 --> 00:14:39,295
‎把我给高兴坏了
and it made me so happy.

295
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:42,381
‎我可以帮忙啊
I could do that for you!

296
00:14:42,965 --> 00:14:45,175
‎随你怎么抱怨 但过去几个星期
Complain all you want,
but these past few weeks

297
00:14:45,259 --> 00:14:47,553
‎我又看到了雷德从前的影子
I have seen glimpses of the old Red.

298
00:14:47,636 --> 00:14:50,472
‎那种火焰 那种激情 我很想念他
The fire, the passion. I miss him.

299
00:14:51,181 --> 00:14:52,224
‎他退休了
He's retired.

300
00:14:52,808 --> 00:14:55,102
‎但他还活着
But he's still alive.

301
00:14:55,185 --> 00:14:56,812
‎你不能一整天
You can't spend all day

302
00:14:56,896 --> 00:15:00,482
‎都在园子里鼓捣番茄
scraping around in your garden,
playing with your tomatoes.

303
00:15:00,566 --> 00:15:04,695
‎-你喜欢我的番茄！
‎-你的番茄太小了！
-You love my tomatoes!
-Your tomatoes are small!

304
00:15:09,575 --> 00:15:10,784
‎你头上全是汗
Your head is sweaty.

305
00:15:13,037 --> 00:15:15,039
‎你的胸口起伏得厉害
-Your chest is heaving.
-[Kitty moans]

306
00:15:16,081 --> 00:15:18,959
["Tell Me Something Good"
by Chaka Khan playing]

307
00:15:19,043 --> 00:15:20,961
<i>♪ Tell me something good… ♪</i>

308
00:15:21,712 --> 00:15:24,465
‎看来退休的日子结束了
Well, so much for a quiet retirement.

309
00:15:24,548 --> 00:15:27,927
‎管道很久没进毛刷刷了
There's no more lint in my dryer filter.

310
00:15:28,010 --> 00:15:29,803
[both laughing]

311
00:15:29,887 --> 00:15:31,347
‎我现在出来安全不？
Is it safe to come out?

312
00:15:32,389 --> 00:15:33,390
‎雪莉
Sherri.

313
00:15:35,142 --> 00:15:38,562
‎我正洗澡呢 刚完事 你俩就开始折腾
I was taking a shower. When I got done,
you guys were dirty doggin' it,

314
00:15:38,646 --> 00:15:40,940
‎我就在里面窝着 等暴风雨结束
so I just hunkered down
and rode out the storm.

315
00:15:41,523 --> 00:15:43,692
‎我就说听见冲马桶的声音了
I told you I heard the toilet flush.

316
00:15:45,694 --> 00:15:49,573
‎抱歉 我就是上来梳洗
‎准备赴一场不该赴的约会
Sorry, I was only up here 'cause I was
getting ready for this mistake of a date.

317
00:15:49,657 --> 00:15:50,783
‎约会？
A date?

318
00:15:50,866 --> 00:15:53,160
‎蓝色米亚达 胡塞…要跟上剧情呀
Blue Miata, Houliha… Keep up.

319
00:15:54,119 --> 00:15:57,373
‎我倒是难得有这种机会思考
But it did give me time to think,
which I never get to do.

320
00:15:57,456 --> 00:15:59,708
‎我到底想要什么？
I mean, what do I want from my life?

321
00:15:59,792 --> 00:16:00,960
‎因为我确定
Because I'm pretty sure

322
00:16:01,043 --> 00:16:05,047
‎躲在邻居家浴室听老头老太嘿咻
‎可不是我的追求
hiding in my neighbor's bathroom
listening to old people bang isn't it.

323
00:16:05,547 --> 00:16:07,883
‎听着像别人啃玉米棒子
Sounded like somebody was eating
corn on the cob.

324
00:16:09,677 --> 00:16:10,970
‎我是怎么了？
What's wrong with me?

325
00:16:11,553 --> 00:16:14,848
‎为什么我总是不断犯同样的错误？
Why do I keep making the same mistake
over and over?

326
00:16:14,932 --> 00:16:19,395
‎哦 亲爱的 别这么难为自己
Oh, honey. Go easy on yourself.

327
00:16:19,937 --> 00:16:22,064
‎你有一份稳定的工作
You have a steady job.

328
00:16:22,147 --> 00:16:25,901
‎你一个人养育了两个好孩子
You are raising two wonderful kids
all on your own.

329
00:16:25,985 --> 00:16:27,736
‎你很棒
You are amazing.

330
00:16:28,237 --> 00:16:31,115
‎-凯蒂 你为什么要骗她？
‎-雷德…
-Kitty, why are you lying to her?
-Red…

331
00:16:31,699 --> 00:16:32,825
‎但他没得说错
But he's not wrong.

332
00:16:32,908 --> 00:16:36,370
‎或许可以先把男人放在一边
Okay, maybe it's time
to take a break from the fellas

333
00:16:36,453 --> 00:16:38,789
‎体验一下独立的感觉
and see what it's like on your own.

334
00:16:38,872 --> 00:16:40,374
‎孤身一人 感觉好可怕
Being alone sounds scary.

335
00:16:40,457 --> 00:16:42,710
‎你不是一个人 你还有我们
Well, you're not alone. You've got us.

336
00:16:42,793 --> 00:16:43,627
‎我们？
Us?

337
00:16:44,211 --> 00:16:46,130
‎你现在心情应该好点了吧
You'd think you'd be
in a better mood right now.

338
00:16:47,214 --> 00:16:49,633
[rock music playing]

339
00:16:50,884 --> 00:16:52,720
‎欢迎来到电影之夜
Welcome to movie night.

340
00:16:52,803 --> 00:16:54,972
‎今晚肯定超赞 首先
It's gonna be pretty major,
so to kick things off right

341
00:16:55,055 --> 00:16:57,933
‎我给你们每人准备了一盒葡萄干麦片
I got everyone
their own box of Raisin Bran.

342
00:16:58,017 --> 00:17:00,811
‎葡萄干麦片！
Raisin Bran! Raisin Bran!
Raisin Bran! [chuckles]

343
00:17:00,894 --> 00:17:02,521
‎大家都喜欢 记得吗？
Everybody loves it. Remember?

344
00:17:02,604 --> 00:17:05,190
‎不是吗？这事没发生吗？
No? Did that not happen?

345
00:17:06,233 --> 00:17:08,152
‎你知道谁喜欢葡萄干麦片吗？
‎我表哥 他给布雷特法弗…
Oh, you know who loves Raisin Bran?

346
00:17:08,235 --> 00:17:09,653
‎你知道谁喜欢葡萄干麦片吗？
‎我表哥 他给布雷特法弗…
My cousin who did Brett Favre's--

347
00:17:09,737 --> 00:17:11,155
‎别
Do not.

348
00:17:12,489 --> 00:17:14,825
‎-那我们要看什么？
‎-我最喜欢的电影
-So what are we watching?
-Uh, my favorite movie.

349
00:17:14,908 --> 00:17:16,744
‎《疯狂店员》凯文史密斯主演
‎我可喜欢他了
<i>Clerks, </i>starring Kevin Smith.

350
00:17:16,827 --> 00:17:18,495
‎《疯狂店员》凯文史密斯主演
‎我可喜欢他了
[chuckles] I'll take a slice of that.

351
00:17:20,456 --> 00:17:21,749
‎好吧…
[both] Okay…

352
00:17:24,418 --> 00:17:27,296
‎嗨 音乐电视台 我是利奥
<i>Hey, MTV. I'm Leo, man.</i>

353
00:17:27,963 --> 00:17:29,923
‎我今年74了
<i>I'm 74 years young,</i>

354
00:17:30,007 --> 00:17:33,135
‎演《真实世界》特别合适
<i>and I'd be perfect</i>
<i>for </i>The Real World, <i>man.</i>

355
00:17:33,218 --> 00:17:34,219
‎这是什么呀？
What's this?

356
00:17:34,887 --> 00:17:37,056
‎不知道 应该是《疯狂店员》才对
I don't know.
It was supposed to be <i>Clerks.</i>

357
00:17:37,139 --> 00:17:38,640
‎说到个人趣事
Fun facts about me.

358
00:17:40,309 --> 00:17:43,103
‎我从过山车上摔下来三回
I've fallen off of
three roller coasters, man.

359
00:17:44,521 --> 00:17:47,107
‎其实是四回 如果算上第四回
Well, four, if you count the fourth one.

360
00:17:47,191 --> 00:17:48,567
[TV clicks off]

361
00:17:49,151 --> 00:17:51,111
‎还是别看了
Uh… forget movies.

362
00:17:51,195 --> 00:17:53,238
‎有人有趣事分享吗？
Does anyone have
any funny stories to share?

363
00:17:53,822 --> 00:17:54,782
[choking]

364
00:17:54,865 --> 00:17:55,741
‎很好 内特
Oh good, Nate.

365
00:17:56,617 --> 00:17:59,536
‎不 他吃葡萄干麦片噎着了 太干了
No. He's choking on the Raisin Bran.
It's too dry.

366
00:17:59,620 --> 00:18:01,163
‎给他拿点喝的
Give him something to drink.

367
00:18:03,290 --> 00:18:04,208
‎不用吸管了！
Forget the straw!

368
00:18:05,793 --> 00:18:07,461
‎好了 宝贝 喝吧
Okay. Drink, baby, drink.

369
00:18:07,544 --> 00:18:09,588
[slurping]

370
00:18:09,671 --> 00:18:11,799
‎好了 顺下去了
I'm good. It went down.

371
00:18:12,299 --> 00:18:14,426
[choking]

372
00:18:14,510 --> 00:18:16,345
‎不行 你得这样 清出来…
No, you gotta clear it out like this.
Like…

373
00:18:16,428 --> 00:18:17,763
‎不行 你得这样 清出来…
-[coughs]
-[coughs]

374
00:18:17,846 --> 00:18:21,558
‎莉亚 你应该当活动策划人
‎这真是太有意思了
Leia, you should be an event planner.
This is so fun.

375
00:18:22,184 --> 00:18:23,310
‎对不起！
Gah! I'm sorry!

376
00:18:24,103 --> 00:18:26,522
‎我真的希望今晚能完美
I really wanted this
to be a perfect night.

377
00:18:27,106 --> 00:18:28,440
‎算了
[scoffs] Forget it.

378
00:18:30,317 --> 00:18:31,318
‎莉亚…
Leia…

379
00:18:33,320 --> 00:18:34,696
‎别吃了
Hey, stop eating that.

380
00:18:34,780 --> 00:18:35,739
‎我饿了
I'm hungry!

381
00:18:37,449 --> 00:18:39,910
‎嘿 戏精 刚才怎么回事？
Yo, drama queen. What was up with that?

382
00:18:40,494 --> 00:18:41,537
‎我太假了
I'm a fraud.

383
00:18:41,620 --> 00:18:43,247
‎我根本没看过《疯狂店员》
I've never even seen <i>Clerks</i>.

384
00:18:43,330 --> 00:18:45,749
‎我最喜欢的电影是…《威鲸闯天关》
My favorite movie is… <i>Free Willy</i>.

385
00:18:47,668 --> 00:18:48,710
‎讲的是一个小男孩
It's about a boy.

386
00:18:50,045 --> 00:18:51,046
‎还有他的鲸鱼
And his whale.

387
00:18:51,964 --> 00:18:52,965
‎然后呢？
So?

388
00:18:53,715 --> 00:18:55,467
‎他想把鲸鱼送回大海
So he tries to get Willy
back in the ocean.

389
00:18:55,551 --> 00:18:58,554
‎不 我是想问 你为什么那么激动？
No. I mean,
why did you melt down in there?

390
00:19:00,097 --> 00:19:01,098
‎就是…
It's just…

391
00:19:01,932 --> 00:19:04,226
‎我感觉跟你们在一起 我很格格不入
I feel like an imposter in this group.

392
00:19:04,726 --> 00:19:07,563
‎你们那么酷 那么要好
You guys are all so close and so cool,

393
00:19:08,397 --> 00:19:10,274
‎只有我
and I'm just me.

394
00:19:10,357 --> 00:19:13,152
‎如果你怀疑自己 记住
If you're ever doubting yourself,
just remember,

395
00:19:13,986 --> 00:19:15,988
‎你家地下室超赞的
you have a <i>killer</i> basement.

396
00:19:17,573 --> 00:19:19,533
‎我还以为你会说些更好听的呢
I thought you were gonna say
something way nicer.

397
00:19:20,742 --> 00:19:22,661
‎你知道这里有多无聊吗？
You know how boring it is around here?

398
00:19:22,744 --> 00:19:27,374
‎上礼拜 我们往河里扔了一根棍子
‎然后朝它扔别的棍子
Last week, we threw a stick in the creek
and tried to hit it with other sticks.

399
00:19:28,167 --> 00:19:29,626
‎内特管这叫“棒打棒棒”
Nate called it Stick Stick.

400
00:19:33,672 --> 00:19:35,591
‎傻瓜 不光是你家地下室
It's not just about your basement, dummy.

401
00:19:35,674 --> 00:19:38,302
‎如果是我让你有压力 咱们俩好得很
If you're stressing about me, we're good.

402
00:19:39,469 --> 00:19:42,264
‎如果你担心自己不合群
And if you're worried about
fitting in with everyone else,

403
00:19:42,347 --> 00:19:44,433
‎那你算找到不合群的人了
you found the people who don't fit in.

404
00:19:45,392 --> 00:19:46,476
‎我可是个中王者
And I am their queen.

405
00:19:48,395 --> 00:19:49,688
‎我没交过像你这样的朋友
Never had a friend like you.

406
00:19:50,939 --> 00:19:51,940
‎我知道
I know.

407
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:54,401
‎伙计们！
Guys!

408
00:19:54,484 --> 00:19:56,987
‎我们在这个袋子里又找到另一个袋子
We just found another bag inside this bag.

409
00:19:57,946 --> 00:19:58,989
‎袋中袋
<i>Bag </i>bag!

410
00:20:00,449 --> 00:20:01,909
‎我刚想到的
I just came up with that.

411
00:20:02,409 --> 00:20:05,579
[rock music playing]

412
00:20:06,663 --> 00:20:09,958
‎袋中袋里可真有好货
The stuff in that <i>bag </i>bag was <i>good </i>good.

413
00:20:11,168 --> 00:20:14,004
‎那也比不过《威鲸闯天关》我喜欢
Not as good as <i>Free Willy.</i> I love it.

414
00:20:14,087 --> 00:20:17,007
‎冷静 这就是
‎鲸鱼版《ET外星人》而已
Check yourself.
This is just<i> E.T.</i> with a whale.

415
00:20:18,842 --> 00:20:21,345
‎虽然不是《疯狂店员》
‎但也挺可爱的 对吧？
I know it's not <i>Clerks</i>,
but it's kinda cute, right?

416
00:20:21,428 --> 00:20:24,097
‎就好像我是那个男孩
‎鲸鱼威利是橡皮筋
It's like… I'm the boy

417
00:20:25,224 --> 00:20:26,850
‎就好像我是那个男孩
‎鲸鱼威利是橡皮筋
and Willy's the rubber band.

418
00:20:27,684 --> 00:20:28,685
‎我终于懂了
I get it now.

419
00:20:29,978 --> 00:20:31,813
‎莉亚 威利会成功吗？
Leia, is Willy gonna make it?

420
00:20:31,897 --> 00:20:33,690
‎ET外星人成功了吗？
Did E.T. make it?

421
00:20:35,442 --> 00:20:36,693
‎-加油 威利
‎-加油
-Come on, Willy.
-Come on.

422
00:20:36,777 --> 00:20:37,611
‎你能行
You can do it.

423
00:20:37,694 --> 00:20:39,321
‎-你能行 来吧
‎-好的 威利
-You got this. Come on.
-Yes, Willy.

424
00:20:39,404 --> 00:20:40,405
‎耶！
[all] Yeah!

425
00:20:40,489 --> 00:20:41,657
‎他成功了！
He made it!

426
00:20:41,740 --> 00:20:43,575
-[movie score swells]
-[laughing]

427
00:20:50,499 --> 00:20:51,875
‎就当没发生
This never happened.

428
00:20:53,961 --> 00:20:55,462
‎嗨 福尔曼先生
Hey, Mr. Forman.

429
00:20:55,963 --> 00:20:57,381
‎这是我在面包车里发现的
I found this in my van.

430
00:20:57,881 --> 00:20:59,591
‎看来我有一个神秘的仰慕者
Looks like I have a secret admirer.

431
00:20:59,675 --> 00:21:01,593
‎是你 对吧？
[whispers] It's you, isn't it?

432
00:21:02,678 --> 00:21:05,889
‎不过是一件衬衣 别搞得这么诡异
It's just a shirt. Don't make it weird.

433
00:21:05,973 --> 00:21:07,057
‎我没有
I'm not.

434
00:21:08,892 --> 00:21:11,103
‎-我能叫你雷德叔叔吗？
‎-出去
-Can I call you Uncle Red?
-Get out.

435
00:21:14,481 --> 00:21:15,482
‎再见 雷德叔叔
Bye, Uncle Red.

436
00:21:19,569 --> 00:21:20,445
‎凯蒂
Kitty.

437
00:21:22,948 --> 00:21:25,158
‎你就穿这身跟男人分手？
<i>That's </i>what you're wearing
to break up with a guy?

438
00:21:26,952 --> 00:21:29,788
‎那泳池派对得穿成什么样啊
I can't imagine
what you would wear to a pool party.

439
00:21:32,457 --> 00:21:34,584
‎说什么呢？这是我的葬礼装
What? This is my funeral outfit.

440
00:21:35,377 --> 00:21:37,879
‎这是跟别人道永别的衣裳
It's what I wear
to say goodbye to someone forever.

441
00:21:37,963 --> 00:21:39,339
[car horn honking]

442
00:21:39,840 --> 00:21:42,426
‎肯定是他了 老天 我好紧张
That's him. Oh God, I'm just so nervous.

443
00:21:42,509 --> 00:21:43,969
‎我吃了一堆头发
I've eaten a ton of my hair.

444
00:21:45,387 --> 00:21:46,888
‎之前比现在高多了
This was so much higher.

445
00:21:46,972 --> 00:21:47,973
‎别这样
Well, stop that.

446
00:21:48,557 --> 00:21:51,018
‎-你很坚强
‎-嗯
-You are strong.
-Yeah.

447
00:21:51,101 --> 00:21:52,644
‎-你很独立
‎-嗯
-You're independent.
-Yeah.

448
00:21:52,728 --> 00:21:53,729
‎-你还年轻…吧
‎-嗯
You're still young…

449
00:21:53,812 --> 00:21:54,771
‎-你还年轻…吧
‎-嗯
-Yeah.
-…ish.

450
00:21:56,189 --> 00:21:59,318
‎-他也就有一个高级喇叭
‎-嗯
-He is just some guy with a fancy horn.
-Right.

451
00:21:59,401 --> 00:22:00,944
‎好了 去吧
Now, go.

452
00:22:01,486 --> 00:22:03,155
‎甩掉那家伙！
Dump that chump!

453
00:22:03,238 --> 00:22:05,532
‎《瑞奇莱克》节目上就这么说
That's what they say on <i>Ricki Lake.</i>

454
00:22:05,615 --> 00:22:06,450
[laughs]

455
00:22:23,925 --> 00:22:26,762
‎我想着让你看看我的性感样
‎应该挺不赖的
I thought it would be fun
for you to see me look this sexy.

456
00:22:27,346 --> 00:22:28,680
[rock music playing]

457
00:22:33,185 --> 00:22:37,606
[rock music playing]

458
00:23:08,595 --> 00:23:13,141
‎字幕翻译：Zeo Niu

